{"tid":1460554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冇乜事唔好北上支那之瘋狂抽check","createTime":"2019-08-13T03:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T10:52:44.000Z","uid":182003,"like":109,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"322a40e9a160f77537e439715869001cf115fa04","tid":1460554,"uid":182003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"小弟工作需要每星期都要北上支那<br />\n設立黑屏風捉人入去check手機相信大家呢幾個星期都睇到唔少報導<br />\n過去一兩個星期都仲未算捉得幾嚴重，起碼我過幾次都未見過有人被捉<br />\n但今日係福田過關，經過有公安守個樽頸位，左右隔離有3，4個人俾公安的走左<br />\n望過去黑屏風果邊有十幾個人排緊隊等被check<br />\n另一方面係西九過關嘅同事都話呢幾個星期一直未set黑屏風嘅西九關都已經有<br />\n以我觀察同同事經歷，係老中青，任何顏色衫都會捉<br />\n我個禿頭廢老同事都俾公安的左入去，佢仲話公安連佢份大公報都要收<br />\n所以提提各位真.香港人，冇咩事真係唔好北上支那喇<br />\n真係要北上嘅都唔該要做好準備，唔好帶用黎發夢嘅手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc198d7658f4f448f8ee2488fb97c5957452d58e","tid":1460554,"uid":182003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25ec47fb47f7ff984c77eef47faeb650825dbdba","tid":1460554,"uid":112901,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:38:48.000Z","msg":"清有冇被拮手指"},{"pid":"23d786fd33ecaddc519d8fb6e125bfde702d9b64","tid":1460554,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"辭工啦"},{"pid":"d265b49ea07554cbd0255555c013ea9957c25477","tid":1460554,"uid":271199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"今個月陪老母上支那，被check 袋 ，查問番去咩事，無查手機無收集DNA，番黎時候好驚訝竟然無check我。所以要返支那就盡量帶衫同埋日用品啦。"},{"pid":"51a6f9119c7da24d12de864059a42fcea9816abe","tid":1460554,"uid":187253,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:48:04.000Z","msg":"早幾日上咗去一轉做嘢<br />\n見前邊2個黑衫畀人欄住要入黑屏風<br />\n來回都有<br />\n<br />\n大家要上去都記住帶士啤電話，除咗蝗app<br />\n唔好裝其他嘢，最好log out埋Apple cloud/Google account<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99ba9ba2a5b0418a28af27fb74e6bfeaa8bca48","tid":1460554,"uid":182003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25ec47fb47f7ff984c77eef47faeb650825dbdba","tid":1460554,"uid":112901,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:38:48.000Z","msg":"清有冇被拮手指"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:43:46.000Z","msg":"我好彩冇俾公安的走，被的走同事話只係check左袋，多謝關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f941b1af0debf6e56b28a5337c2ddb9e45f6118","tid":1460554,"uid":182003,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:57:54.000Z","msg":"推,要俾多啲逼於無奈要北上支那嘅手足知<br />\n同時俾港豬知道下冇犯法一樣出事"},{"pid":"c8f710d830a4f3d6b880b454ee79b505fc9d10d2","tid":1460554,"uid":182003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d42cf20610c8790e93d2f0c758ca3d72b101c748","tid":1460554,"uid":53238,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:11:18.000Z","msg":"屌喇星月尾要上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f2d4de4fd6fb57c6e62a27d2cad189f2540ee2","tid":1460554,"uid":182003,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d42cf20610c8790e93d2f0c758ca3d72b101c748","tid":1460554,"uid":53238,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:11:18.000Z","msg":"屌喇星月尾要上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:30:32.000Z","msg":"帶部後備手機，唔好著得太光鮮<br />\n我覺得有啲幫助，今日特登著件勁殘嘅灰T冇俾公安的走<br />\n大目標應該係抽後生仔，有個淺藍衫後生仔行過左個公安都追住的返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990d6b8d70136221cb3c21ac143625949ccd9b1e","tid":1460554,"uid":182003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔記得提埋<br />\n唔好以為入境支那過到關就冇事<br />\n出境支那都會有黑屏風恭候<br />\n暫時我自己fact check過所有常用陸路關口<br />\n福田﹑皇崗﹑羅湖﹑西九都會有<br />\n之前有空姐朋友飛上海話上海機場都有"},{"pid":"c5efbd20abbd8df57f07ff12d4cfb979466dcba3","tid":1460554,"uid":182003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:00:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9a51cceecc4af8517fde8bdb7930708aa880d61","tid":1460554,"uid":195268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:07:39.000Z","msg":"今日係無差別入個屏風查，入境出境都查。上星期個屏風入面都係得兩三個公安，今日六七個，每個都會開手機，入去只係睇相簿。（建議電話轉用英文介面）"},{"pid":"a51afbffbf41248b3325ed48340d8fd44939bcf9","tid":1460554,"uid":195268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"990d6b8d70136221cb3c21ac143625949ccd9b1e","tid":1460554,"uid":182003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔記得提埋<br />\n唔好以為入境支那過到關就冇事<br />\n出境支那都會有黑屏風恭候<br />\n暫時我自己fact check過所有常用陸路關口<br />\n福田﹑皇崗﹑羅湖﹑西九都會有<br />\n之前有空姐朋友飛上海話上海機場都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:08:23.000Z","msg":"加多個深圳灣"},{"pid":"832d62c1e8dddad18008401808a336a47516d4c5","tid":1460554,"uid":263337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:12:22.000Z","msg":"返大陸？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d37f6b2e37f1cb6d0a6a7a70af46567afe6882","tid":1460554,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"之前朋友帶gip 過落馬洲，裏面有藥油，成箱被扣查，第二朝先拎得返。電話被人查（提早叫佢拔走Sd card 放入小褲袋)，android 電話較訪客mode 博佢唔識用，iPhone 唔知<br />\n<br />\n真係要上就帶dummy 機啦<br />\n<br />\n---------離線通訊神器---------<br />\nAndroid 版Airdrop：Files by Google<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457044</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Google Play: Files by Google 連結</strong> <a href=\"https://g.co/filesgo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Ffilesgo&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y94Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=6